room_title: Escape room "Escape from London" by Can You Escape? in Tampa
room_description: In a uniquely London-themed room, you’ll explore the rich history of England's most famous King and Queens while unearthing some interestingly 'British' facts to escape. It will take a keen eye, some ingenuity and help from Shakespeare, Big Ben and the Rolling Stones for you to escape this fun-filled room.
